 <name>Vistle</name>
 <summary>Interactive scientific visualization system</summary>
 <description>
  <p>
      Vistle is an interactive visualization system for scientific with a focus on Virtual Reality.
      Workflows can be created and modified with a graphical editor.
      All nodes of a cluster can be used for data-parallel processing,
      and several clusters can be chained for distributed workflows.
      Remote-rendering is an integral part of the visualization pipeline.
  </p>
 </description>
